-------------------------<br>
I do like the idea of giving mages ports, but maybe do this with a bit of a 'twist'. Allow mages to summon an object (similar to the orb for JaggedPine, or the FG Port to Twilight). Each object can go to a single location, and will remain in game for up to 15 min after casting. Once the mage drops the item, the timer starts. So a mage could actually carry the item into a dungeon and have a basic form of Evac if necessary. The timer and functionality of the item would begin once the item is dropped. Each object can be used 6 times before vanishing.<br>
<br>
Spell line would be called Summon Portal.<br>
